# Plan Feature Skill

This skill performs research-driven planning for new roadmap features.

## Configuration

- **Model**: claude-sonnet-4.5
- **Tool**: claude-code
- **Interactive**: false
- **Provider**: anthropic

## Capabilities

This skill coordinates multiple phases to create implementation plans:
1. Research existing codebase and patterns
2. Synthesize findings into architectural decisions
3. Generate detailed implementation plans with tasks

## Usage


This skill operates in foreground mode with sequential phase execution.


## Runner Files

- [research-runner.md](research-runner.md) - Research orchestration
- [synthesis-runner.md](synthesis-runner.md) - Synthesis orchestration
- [planning-runner.md](planning-runner.md) - Planning orchestration

## Models

- Fast tier: claude-haiku-4
- Standard tier: claude-sonnet-4.5
- Deep tier: claude-opus-4
